  "input": {
    "passage": "I have a bag. My bag is here. I see a book, a pen, and a pencil in my bag. I have a ruler and an eraser too. The pen is on the book. I look at my ruler and my eraser. I like my bag and my book very much. I see my pen, my pencil, my ruler, and my eraser every day.",
